                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-12-off71 t17860222-12-cd72"></join>, one bag, value 6 d. one basket, value 12 d. and one hundred and fifty pounds weight of Russia tallow, value 4 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17860222-12-victim229" type="victimName">
